{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"headervaluebyname\">\n<span id=\"id1\"></span><h1>headerValueByName</h1>\n<p>Extracts the value of the HTTP request header with the given name.</p>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"signature\">\n<h2>Signature</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">headerValueByName</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">headerName</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Symbol</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Directive1</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> \n<span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">headerValueByName</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">headerName</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Directive1</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> \n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"description\">\n<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>The name can be given as a <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">String</span></tt> or as a <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">Symbol</span></tt>. If no header with a matching name is found the request\nis rejected with a <tt class=\"docutils literal\"><span class=\"pre\">MissingHeaderRejection</span></tt>. If the header is expected to be missing in some cases or to customize\nhandling when the header is missing use the <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../optionalHeaderValueByName/#optionalheadervaluebyname\"><em>optionalHeaderValueByName</em></a> directive instead.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"example\">\n<h2>Example</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">val</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">headerValueByName</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;X-User-Id&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span> <span class=\"n\">userId</span> <span class=\"k\">=&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">complete</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;The user is $userId&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"nc\">Get</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;/&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"nc\">RawHeader</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;X-User-Id&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;Joe42&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">check</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">responseAs</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">===</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;The user is Joe42&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"nc\">Get</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;/&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">sealRoute</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">route</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">check</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">status</span> <span class=\"o\">===</span> <span class=\"nc\">BadRequest</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">responseAs</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">===</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;Request is missing required HTTP header &#39;X-User-Id&#39;&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "display_toc": true, "title": "headerValueByName", "sourcename": "", "customsidebar": null, "current_page_name": "documentation/spray-routing/header-directives/headerValueByName", "next": {"link": "../headerValueByType/", "title": "headerValueByType"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["documentation/spray-routing/header-directives/headerValueByType", "headerValueByType", "N", "next"], ["documentation/spray-routing/header-directives/headerValue", "headerValue", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "Documentation"}, {"link": "../../", "title": "spray-routing"}, {"link": "../../predefined-directives-by-trait/", "title": "Predefined Directives (by trait)"}, {"link": "../", "title": "HeaderDirectives"}], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">headerValueByName</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#signature\">Signature</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#description\">Description</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#example\">Example</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../headerValue/", "title": "headerValue"}, "metatags": ""}